title: Sharon Runner Requests State of Emergency for Los Angeles County (California Senate Republican Caucus)
text: ( Source : California Senate Republican Caucus ) Senator Sharon Runner (R-Antelope Valley) has called upon Governor Brown to declare a State of Emergency in Los Angeles County due to the devastating aftermath of recent flooding and mudslides.
